##Funeral home vehicles transport supplies, Wuhan, Huangpi District Notice: Funeral Director fired

Weixin Signal Wowjiemian

Function introduction, the interface news is China has the influence original financial and economic new media, only serves the independent thinking crowd

Image: Tubo

Source: Huangpi District Government website

Author: Huangpi District Government website

“

On the evening of March 14, the 8:50 of the Huangpi District District Committee and the District Commission for Discipline Inspection found that the wechat group of Haifu community in Jiang'an District reflected that "the community uses funeral parlors to transport group shopping materials" and immediately organized verification and handling.

”

“

On the evening of March 14, the 8:50 of the Huangpi District District Committee and the District Commission for Discipline Inspection found that the wechat group of Haifu community in Jiang'an District reflected that "the community uses funeral parlors to transport group shopping materials" and immediately organized verification and handling.

”

After investigation, at about 3:20 pm on the same day, Lu mou, a social contractor of rural funeral vehicles in Huangpi district, illegally used his contracted funeral vehicles to transport supplies to his relative Chen Mou, who lives in the Haifu Jiangcheng community in Jiang'an District, the goods and materials are purchased by a contractor of the funeral vehicle, not by a community group. Lu's behavior caused adverse social effects.

After the study by the Huangpi District Commission for Discipline Inspection and reported to the District Commission for approval, the Director of the district funeral and interment administration office, Ao Hao, was removed from office and Party discipline was placed on file for review; To instruct the district funeral and interment administration office to terminate the contract with Lu for the operation of funeral vehicles, and investigate the liability for breach of contract according to law.
